Some of your reactions aren’t coming from who you are now…
they’re coming from who you had to be then.
Healing isn’t about fighting that part of you.
It’s about meeting them with compassion and taking the wheel with love. 🤍
•
Your nervous system learned how to survive before it learned how to feel safe.
Awareness changes everything. ✨

